<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Dezir</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-14 16:32:50</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just got one of these last night off of a lego in Lake of Ill Omen.  I must say that this will be a very useful tool for me.  Why?  Because I'm a ranger.  Rangers are the only class that I know of that is capable of becoming invis but have no see invis spell.<BR>
<BR>
So now when I'm guiding someone through a zone that's dangerous to them or to me, I can use the bracer on both of us and then camo both of us.  No more wondering whether or not the person is still with me.</font></td></tr></table>
