<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Shanon</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-10 17:59:31</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hi there.<BR>
Most people clerified this.. but im going to go ahead and say it again.<BR>
I won one on a roll.<BR>
Its AC is not great... but you aren't using it for combat.<BR>
it's a right clickable effect... that you cast.. no mana.. no casting time... infinite casts.<BR>
You can cast on ANYONE and ANYTHING.<BR>
Leave it in your invitory.. and eqeuip between battles to cast. Lasts a good 15 to 20 minutes for me.<BR>
Fun things to do:<BR>
Cast on the guards at NK.... Those invisible KOS people will be in tuff poo there.<BR>
Also... Rangers should be paying HIGH amounts for this.. and rogue's can make off well with it too. Im a warrior..and i love it.. but if i get a GOOD offer... id be willing to sell...<BR>
Trade? Maybe... maybe.. Im on povar... give me a tell if you are interested.<BR>
Shanon Loveheart<BR>
