<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Pertisat</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-18 23:33:46</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Hi all, 23rd level bard here.  I just wanted to say a few things about this bracer.  I was hunting in the sarnak fortress the other night, and the first lego we killed dropped this.  Luckily I won the roll, and i'm extremely happy with this piece.  One of my high lev friends gave me a ruby bracer, and I had a bronze on my other wrist.  With this bracer in place of the bronze, I only lose 1 AC, and gain a great effect.  Maybe the AC loss is more important if you're a higher level player with better equipment, but at my level there is little AC sacrifice.  Yes, I like it a lot.</font></td></tr></table>
